---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Kisan Thapa" description="PhD candidate in Computational Biology and Deep Learning at UMass Boston.">

  <div class="pb-10 border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-zinc-800">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-zinc-50">About</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-10 space-y-5 text-sm text-slate-700 dark:text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
    <p>
      I'm <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-zinc-100">Kisan Thapa</strong>, a PhD candidate in
      Computer Science at the{' '}
      <a
        href="https://www.umb.edu"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-slate-900 dark:text-zinc-100 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-slate-500 dark:hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors"
      >
        University of Massachusetts Boston
      </a>,
      specializing in <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-zinc-100">Computational Biology</strong> and
      <strong class="text-slate-900 dark:text-zinc-100">Deep Learning</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
      My research focuses on developing advanced computational methods — particularly leveraging deep
      learning and graph neural networks — to decipher complex biological systems from omics data.
      I'm interested in how we can encode biological prior knowledge into neural network architectures
      to make models that are not just accurate, but interpretable and scientifically meaningful.
    </p>
    <p>
      I work within the{' '}
      <a
        href="https://sites.google.com/view/umb-network-biology"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-slate-900 dark:text-zinc-100 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-slate-500 dark:hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors"
      >
        Network Biology Laboratory
      </a>{' '}
      under the supervision of{' '}
      <a
        href="https://sites.google.com/view/ozgunbabur"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="text-slate-900 dark:text-zinc-100 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-slate-500 dark:hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors"
      >
        Prof. Özgün Babur
      </a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before my PhD I completed a Bachelor of Computer Engineering at Pokhara University, Nepal.
      That background in systems and software still shapes how I think about research: rigorous
      engineering and good science are not in tension — they reinforce each other.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside research, I write about things I'm learning on the{' '}
      <a
        href="/blog"
        class="text-slate-900 dark:text-zinc-100 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-slate-500 dark:hover:text-zinc-400 transition-colors"
      >
        blog
      </a>{' '}
      — paper reviews, methods breakdowns, and the occasional longer essay on topics that interest me.
    </p>
  </div>

  <section class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 dark:text-zinc-500">Links</h2>
